data.description: Welcome to 20 Winchelsea Court, a one-level home in the charming community of the Villages of Old Landing in Rehoboth Beach, Delaware. This three-bedroom, two-bathroom gem is the epitome of comfort and convenience.  As you step into the home you are greeted by a spacious living room, adorned with a warm fireplace, creating a cozy ambiance for relaxation and entertaining. The formal dining area provides an elegant space for entertaining friends and family. The primary suite is a true retreat, featuring a large walk-in closet and an ensuite bath with a luxurious soaking tub and a stall shower. Picture yourself unwinding in this private oasis after a long day. The house boasts a separate laundry room leading to an attached garage, ensuring convenience in your daily routines. Step outside to the rear patio, a perfect spot for enjoying the fresh air and hosting outdoor activities.   This community gem also offers access to a refreshing community pool, adding a delightful option for leisure and recreation. This residence is strategically located, providing a short drive to the beach, bay, shopping, and dining. Embrace the coastal lifestyle with easy access to the best that Rehoboth Beach has to offer. Whether you are sizing down, settling down, or seeking a cozy retreat, this home is designed to cater to your needs. Don't miss the opportunity to make this delightful property in the Villages of Old Landing your new home. Experience the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and coastal living.
